@startuml
title UC05 - Prediction Screen Flow
start
:Open match detail;
if (Logged in?) then (yes)
  :Select team for each criterion;
  if (Before deadline and match not cancelled?) then (yes)
    :Submit or edit prediction;
    :Show success and updated statistics;
  else (no)
    :Show locked/unavailable message;
  endif
else (no)
  :Prompt login;
endif
stop
